MESSAGE.value:
Small bug fixed in config.js that prevented a resource from loading.
Documentation added to editor.js.
Started writing javadoc for the classes, and created javadoc directory to check in.
Moving javadoc to the wiki area.

Fix for Issue 3 (http://code.google.com/p/ck-jsf-editor/issues/detail?id=3).
Added 3 attributes to editor tag: saveMethod, ajax, and update. When the save button on the editor is pressed, the following happens: If saveMethod is specified, an ajax request is made and the MethodExpression is fired off and all elements listed in the update attribute are updated, otherwise if ajax is true (default) the save button is disabled, otherwise (if ajax is false) it does a full form submission.
Change to editor.js to fix re-rendering problem.
Added change listener for form submits.
Fixed big bug with not finding correct ckeditor basepath when jsf page was not at top level.
Editor wasn't working with the latest version of primefaces due to custom script header element not having "name" attribute. Fixed.
Added css loading for content area of editor.
